name: THRAIYUKTA ORGANIZATION
briefDescription: Thraiyukta Organization is located in Prakasam, Andhra Pradesh. THRAIYUKTA is a registered organization registered under the Societies Registration Act 2001. The operational area covers the whole of India with a specific focus in the state of Andhra Pradesh and Telangana. The Organization is involved in the variety of activities in view of fostering the development of the marginalized and the poor.
